            "value": "Duplicate"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "要望を入力して「送信」ボタンを押せば、チャッピーにパックの新規作成や修正を依頼できます。要望に沿った叩き台を手早く作ってくれる感じです。参考にして修正しながらお楽しみください。AI利用券1枚で1回の送信が可能です。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Type your request and hit “Send” — Chappy will help you make or edit a pack! You’ll get a quick draft based on your idea, so feel free to tweak and have fun with it. One AI ticket lets you send one request."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "訪問先、日程、目的、人数、気候、アクティビティなどの要望をたくさん列記してください（最大%lld文字）\n\n（例）海外旅行5泊6日、イタリア、スペイン、家族4人、雨天も想定、救急用品も持参": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Feel free to list lots of details — destination, dates, purpose, group size, weather, activities, anything! (Up to %lld characters)\n\nExample: 6-day family trip to Italy and Spain, four people, expect rain, pack a first-aid kit."
          }
        }
      }
    },
